ActFarm Products Agencies Act
PrecisAppointment of BDO Canada LLP of Ottawa, Ontario, to be the auditor for the Chicken Farmers of Canada, to audit its accounts and financial transactions and report thereupon to Chicken Farmers of Canada, the Farm Products Council of Canada and the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food, for the five fiscal years ending December 31, 2020.
